name: THE TICKLE - Issue #34
description:
Art zine focused on Tezos NFT artists and writers.

Issue #34 features artists Uberneath (@uberneath), Andrew Brereton (@aebrer) & Maximiliano Alejandro Zas (@por_zas), with a poem by Joely Arrowsmith (@joelyarrowsmith)

Created by artists Wily Guys (@guyswily) & Theo Horsmeier (@THorsmeier) and writer Joanne Rush (@JonicolaRush).
